videos.description: Illinois scores the first points of the game as RB Dre Brown cuts to the outside and outruns the defense for a 10-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Illinois strikes first on Brown's TD run) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Illinois strikes first on Brown's TD run

videos.description: Rutgers converts on third down as QB Johnny Langan drops a pass between two defenders and finds Mohamed Jabbie for the 31-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Langan threads the needle for Rutgers TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Langan threads the needle for Rutgers TD

videos.description: Before the Rutgers and Illinois game, the two teams have a clap off.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rutgers and Illinois have a clap off pregame) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rutgers and Illinois have a clap off pregame

videos.description: Illinois QB Brandon Peters rips of a 54-yard gain and on the very next play, Dre Brown takes it into the end zone for the two-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF Highlight (Peters' 54-yard scamper sets up Illinois TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Peters' 54-yard scamper sets up Illinois TD

videos.description: Illinois QB Brandon Peters goes deep and connects with Josh Imatorbhebhe who takes it to the house for a 52-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Illinois airs it out for 52-yard TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Illinois airs it out for 52-yard TD

videos.description: Rutgers QB Johnny Langan has his pass picked off by Dele Harding who takes it back 55 yards untouched for Illinois' second defensive touchdown of the game.
